tiny Beast LLM design

A useful formulation could be:

layer 1: fixed basis vectors

The 7 tokens above are hand-defined and never drift.

layer 2: 666-word vocabulary

Every word is assigned:
	•	a dominant basis relation
	•	optional secondary relations
	•	maybe a strength or blend

Example, very roughly:

