Not literal arithmetic for all cases, but a structured semantic map.

layer 3: phrase composition

The tiny LLM composes meanings from these relations rather than depending only on giant emergent embeddings.

That could make a much smaller model surprisingly coherent, especially for local command and teaching use.

why this helps cheap hardware

A 666-word constrained language plus fixed semantic anchors means:
