	•	easier finetuning
	•	easier interpretability
	•	easier synthetic training data generation

In other words, instead of trying to fit all of English into a tiny local model, Beast gives the model a disciplined operating language.

That is exactly the sort of thing that could make a tiny local model actually useful.

