beast general purpose ai llm doc v0.1

purpose

define the first beast general purpose ai design

goal:
	•	run locally
	•	work on phone-class hardware
	•	operate inside beast
	•	handle beast-native tasks and ordinary personal tasks
	•	remain inspectable
