6. tool layer

the assistant should not only answer
it should act through explicit tools

examples:
	•	call contact
	•	send text
	•	open artifact
	•	run generator
	•	rate artifact
	•	search doc
	•	search address book
	•	inspect command history

principle:

reason in llm
act through tools


